player for several years and in all that time I have managed to level up
my dwarf warrior to teh whopping level of 35!! Well actually, I got to
36 once but died almost immediately after the ding! LOL

With all the new zones and stuff what is you advice for a warrior of my
level and of fairly meager means. I only play about 6 or 7 hours a week.
